{"word":"ἀπαλλακτέος","slug":"ἀπαλλακτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπαλλακτέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀπαλλάσσω'><el>ἀπαλλάσσω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>one must release from</i>, <el>τινά τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>) <i>one must withdraw from, get rid of</i>, <el>τινός</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}